        {
            "title": "Investing.com本週精選個股",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/GQcDb8ntU.u8og0ujZxDlw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEAB20CL_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 美國股市本週看來將大幅收高,因中東緊張局勢出現明顯緩和跡象。這一消息導致相關個股出現強勁走勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以下是Investing.com本週精選個股:</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>石油股</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首先當然是石油股,截至週五美國東部時間13:11,埃克森美孚下跌4.6%、雪佛龍下跌3.3%、西方石油下跌6.2%、馬拉松石油下跌5%、德文能源下跌5.4%。所有這些個股本週都將收低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">週五的走勢是在伊朗外交部長阿拉格奇在X平台上表示之後出現的:「配合黎巴嫩停火,所有商業船隻通過霍爾木茲海峽的通道在停火剩餘期間完全開放。」</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>航空股</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">能源價格下跌使航空股走勢相反,週五延續本週漲勢,美國航空目前上漲5.4%、聯合航空跳漲8.3%、達美航空攀升4.3%、捷藍航空上漲7.4%、西南航空上漲7%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-d0d01107-2b15-3f47-b1b5-5aff7cdc980b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這波漲勢源於對燃料成本下降的預期提振了該板塊的市場情緒。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>Netflix</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與今日趨勢相反的是<span><span>Netflix</span></span>,該股暴跌逾10%,本週看來將收低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這家串流媒體巨頭公布最新季度財報後股價下跌,儘管業績超出市場預期。然而,該公司預測第二季獲利將低於華爾街預期,並宣布董事長里德·哈斯廷斯離職。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>AMD、英特爾、Arm</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span>AMD</span></span>股價在過去一週上漲16.4%,而<span><span><span><span>英特爾</span></span></span></span>飆升逾11%,<span><span><span><span>Arm</span></span></span></span>上漲7%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這些個股上漲是由於人工智慧運算需求強勁,導致科技產業出現CPU短缺。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">伯恩斯坦週四在給客戶的報告中將AMD目標價從235美元上調至265美元,表示該公司正「看好」AMD,因其受惠於伺服器CPU的強勁表現。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>甲骨文</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在去年9月因數據中心建設融資擔憂而開始大幅下跌後,<span><span>甲骨文</span></span>股價本週隨著這些擔憂消退而大幅反彈。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該股在過去一週上漲逾28%,交易價格創下1月底以來的最高水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Citizens分析師帕特里克·沃爾拉文斯在本週的報告中重申對甲骨文的跑贏大盤評級和285美元目標價,此前該公司宣布與Bloom Energy擴大戰略合作夥伴關係。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該分析師還引用甲骨文的估值作為看好該股的理由。</p><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>Strategy</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著比特幣上漲並對中東最新發展作出強勁反應,<span><span><span><span>Strategy</span></span></span></span>(前身為Microstrategy)也獲得上漲動能,週五迄今攀升逾11%。該股在過去一週上漲27.6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">比特幣目前交易於77,594美元附近,當日上漲3.2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/investing-com%E6%9C%AC%E9%80%B1%E7%B2%BE%E9%81%B8%E5%80%8B%E8%82%A1-185705107.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-18 03:11:04",
