        {
            "title": "聯儲會理事沃勒對利率調整表示謹慎 警示長期衝突風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Source: Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/YkJyew8bX.hBu6wqfk3OrQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/46055fd986e15ed85a5c5ab02db42d5a\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Source: Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 聯儲會理事克里斯托弗·沃勒表示，由於伊朗戰爭引發的能源衝擊，他對短期內降低利率的必要性持謹慎態度，並警告衝突可能對通膨產生持久影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">沃勒在周五的演講中勾勒了兩種主要情景，說明伊朗戰爭及其對能源和大宗商品價格的影響將如何影響他的貨幣政策立場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">沃勒表示，在第一種情景下，霍爾木茲海峽重新開放、貿易流動恢復正常，官員將能夠忽略能源價格飆升，並在今年晚些時候專注於疲軟的就業市場。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"聯儲會理事沃勒Source: Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/aDGhIZ.9FjYi2dpfjg8SQg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://media.zenfs.com/no/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/a7628949065602267ac92e842530713c\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">聯儲會理事沃勒Source: Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">沃勒周五在奧本大學表示，在這種情況下，「我的預測是基本通膨將繼續向2%回落，這使我對當前降息持謹慎態度，並更傾向於在今年晚些時候前景更加明朗時，通過降息來支持勞動力市場。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-6e1fd593-7f4b-33c6-9e31-06b063831817-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但他警告稱，原油期貨價格以及整體證券市場可能低估了長期衝突的風險。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">沃勒表示：「就通膨而言，風險在於衝突持續時間越長且能源價格維持高位，這些高成本越可能傳導至其他價格，因為企業在定價時會將高昂的能源投入成本考慮在內。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他指出，如果這種情況發生，而勞動力市場疲軟，這將限制政策應對空間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在這種情形下，沃勒表示，他將在權衡通膨上升與就業市場走弱的風險後決定利率決策。「如果通膨風險高於勞動力市場風險，這可能意味著將政策利率維持在當前目標區間。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">數位聯儲會官員已暗示，他們在4月28日至29日的議息會議上傾向於維持利率不變。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Fed’s Waller Signals Caution On Rates, Sees Risk of Longer War</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%83%E7%90%86%E4%BA%8B%E6%B2%83%E5%8B%92%E5%B0%8D%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E8%AA%BF%E6%95%B4%E8%A1%A8%E7%A4%BA%E8%AC%B9%E6%85%8E-%E8%AD%A6%E7%A4%BA%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%9F%E8%A1%9D%E7%AA%81%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-182735647.html",
